    </label>
    <label>
        <input name="adoption[interested_in_newsletter_feature]" type="radio" value="false">
        No
    </label>
</fieldset>

<p>
    OpenStax and Rice University researchers conduct several pilots and research
    studies. May we contact you about opportunities to participate in future
    pilots or studies?
</p>
<fieldset class="labeled-buttons">
    <label>
        <input checked="checked" name="adoption[interested_in_research]" type="radio" value="true">
